title: Dirichlet energy
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Let $$\varOmega\subseteq\R^n$$ be an open set and $$f\colon\varOmega\to\R$$ differentiable. The //Dirichlet energy// of $$f$$ is defined as

$$
E[f] \coloneqq \frac 1 2 \int_\varOmega \|{\grad f(x)}\|^2 \,\d x.
$$